ODM deputy leader Wycliffe Oparanya has asked the three NASA principals to support Raila Odinga to be the coalition's Presidential flag bearer.Oparnaya who was speaking in Kitale on Saturday, said that Raila is the only one that can beat President Uhuru Kenyatta in the August poll."It is true we are in NASA and from my own thinking, Raila is the best candidate to send Uhuru home due to his experience," he said.Oparanya said the former Prime Minister has fought for the country including the Constitution which is being enjoyed by Kenyans.He also asked water cabinet secretary to join NASA."Eugene will not benefit from the next government if NASA takes over power. Leaders from the Luhya community should all join NASA because this is where the welfare of the luhya nation belongs," he said.